<br>
&quot;Greetings &quot; <br>
*She smiles warmly *<br>
&quot;Welcome to our home. &quot;<br>
<br>
The enchantress floats over and smiles at Trevain and takes a glass.<br>
<br>
&quot;Have you come seeking aid or knowledge , companionship or adventure , for you may find all in this hall .At any rate welcome young Elf be at rest here; &quot; <br>
<br>
