<br>
Whew... nothing like a good battle where we fight five or six things at once and I get to do some real work.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>He watches the others stare at him and he grins broadly</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Oh! Introductions, yes, yes... My name is Leondias Dreamshaper, crazy, foolhardy idiot enchanter. Not to mention the most boring enchanter you'll ever meet.... or is that bored?<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>He fills up his glass with cool water and takes a drink smiling happily.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
So, where are all the noble elves I was told would be joining us? I was expecting a party. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://pages.sbcglobal.net/constiens/leondias-sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cinelene>Cinelene</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://pic6.picturetrail.com/VOL160/1082598/2034507/26016585.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/22/03 7:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=615.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Emerald Family</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>A portal shimmers and opens and out steps The Emerald Family's Wizardress, Cinelene Crystyllherte.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Without words she approaches where Trevian and the strange young wood elf sit, drinking Elven wine...she picks up a glass and looks at with an appreciative gleam in her eyes*</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Raising her glass upward, she speaks</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <br>
<br>
Well met, young elf...I am Cinelene.  Welcome to our home.  Please make yourself comfortable here.  I am sure you will find that which you seek within these walls and this family.<br>
<br>
I see you have already met some of us,<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>she smiles warmly at the elves seated along the hall's tressle table</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
I'm sure more will be coming soon.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>smiling mischieveouly at the young elf, she continues</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <br>
Leondias is here and where he is a party almost invariably starts.<br>
<br>
Tell us something of yourself eh?  We love a good tale...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>She settles back and smiles encouragingly*</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=comitas>comitas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/25/03 2:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=615.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Emerald Family</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>The doors open an inch at a time as Comitas shuffles in.  Noticing his hands, bandaged to the point where you cannot see his fingers, you understand his methodical entrance.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Greetings family.  Yes, the rigors of learning to fish can sometimes lead one to learn to bandage at the same time.  Did you all realize there are small fish with big teeth??&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Realizing everyone's attention has fallen elsewhere, he scans the room.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Ah, a hearty new adventurer has cross our doorstep!  Welcome young soul.  You are amongst a great group of friends.  A family that will give you a smile when sad, a nudge when frozen in fear, and a hand when yours are bandaged!&quot; <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Comitas realizes he needs to sit and listen now...</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;A story a story!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=loricleondegrance>LoricLeondegrance</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/5/03 10:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=615.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Emerald Family</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>As you prepare to tell your tale, you hear the loud footsteps of someone approaching the hall. As the doors open, you see a handsome knight clad in plate armor enter the room. As he greets the other elves within the room, he looks over and takes notice of you.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Well what do we have here? A new recruit perhaps? Well, let's get a look at ya.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>The knight turns and strides over to you, firmly taking a hold of your jaw. Gently he turns your face left to right as he inspects your features.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Looks a little green this one does.&quot; <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>remarks the knight.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>The paladin then reaches for your hands and inspects them.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;But these hands show that you have worked hard in your days. Perhaps with some more training I may take you under my wing as my squire..&quot;<br>
<br>
